name: worry worm
notes:
this listing is for the worry worm pattern only.
the pattern is written in u.s. terms. using a 3.5mm hook will be approx. 13cm high.

each worm is made using aran yarn & a wooden face bead

these are great as bag charms or on keyrings

you can sell your items made using this pattern but please give me credit for designing it.   this pattern and photos within belong to fiona wilkinson (wilky wooly designs) and cannot be sold or distributed. my photos cannot be used to sell your own work
